Fossil record of the family Teiidae. notes on paleobiogeography, current distribution, and habits of the Macroteiids. (Sauria, Scincomorpha, Teiidae)A brief review of the family Teiidae's fossil representation has allowed us to relate some paleobiogeographical data with environmental characteristics in the current distribution of the macroteiids. Their origin and dispersal routes in the course of the geological periods were considered.